Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.10,0:06:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.65,0:06:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來討債了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連同布林格和迪瓦恩德份一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 有兩個隕石接近母艦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.09,0:06:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什...什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.17,0:07:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰斗中別開小差!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧! 在哪!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃開!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦量子波!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找露易絲?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個加速粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.47,0:07:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我們的腦量子波都挑動起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.14,0:07:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的沒錯吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.92,0:07:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷魯亞!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.43,0:07:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從隕石裡出現了MS
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.62,0:07:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種手段不會再中第二次了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.42,0:07:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.13,0:07:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 導彈齊射
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.02,0:07:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.09,0:07:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那...沙慈...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.34,0:07:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個光芒...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.11,0:07:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是幻聽嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.98,0:08:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.23,0:08:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既不是兵器 也不是破壞者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和Gundam已經改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.53,0:08:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.03,0:08:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.22,0:08:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.16,0:08:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沙...沙慈?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.91,0:08:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.35,0:08:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈·庫洛斯洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.60,0:08:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...那個光是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯示的粒子放出量是通常的7倍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.61,0:08:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是TWIN DRIVE的...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.11,0:08:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OO的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.58,0:09:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到了 剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.61,0:09:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲!露易絲!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.74,0:09:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5年前我們也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.22,0:09:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起眺望了地球呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.67,0:09:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候的我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著這顆藍色的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.88,0:10:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定了要來宇宙工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後總有一天 要再一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.78,0:10:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你一起眺望這幅景色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.14,0:10:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當時是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明 已經決定不再見面的...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我們以這樣的形式重逢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.16,0:10:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.49,0:10:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這宇宙裡等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.85,0:10:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧 露易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.38,0:10:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到那些一切的一切都平和安穩的日子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.80,0:10:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.30,0:10:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽到我的聲音了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是加入了天行者組織
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.18,0:10:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是被卷了進來 才在那裡...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.75,0:11:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是因為 這種事情...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.83,0:11:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼為什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.53,0:11:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了實現統一世界 恆久和平
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.72,0:11:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經獻出了這幅身軀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.43,0:11:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了打倒 攪亂世界的天行者組織
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.14,0:11:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後為爸爸和媽媽報仇!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.02,0:11:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要來妨礙我!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是敢來妨礙的話 連你也不會放過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.64,0:11:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪...這很奇怪啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你原來不是這樣的女孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.04,0:11:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼讓你變了的!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.02,0:11:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我自己變了的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.16,0:11:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照自己的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.48,0:11:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在說謊!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我了解的 露易絲...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.16,0:11:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個溫柔的女孩子的!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.79,0:12:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也知道為了去宇宙 而在拼了命地學習!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.09,0:12:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴上很任性
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.81,0:12:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還為了向我撒嬌而耍小孩子脾氣!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.39,0:12:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有其實...是很容易寂寞的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.19,0:12:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是 都知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.22,0:12:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.67,0:12:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.34,0:12:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.82,0:13:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈勒維准尉!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.04,0:13:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.22,0:13:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.09,0:13:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開准尉!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.02,0:13:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢用奇怪的幻術來迷惑准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那部機體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來你果然不擅長接近戰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.33,0:13:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕不上你的機體咯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只會蠻拼火力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.74,0:13:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.52,0:13:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.27,0:14:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎...怎麼可能!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想逃!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.66,0:14:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seraphim!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.14,0:14:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有事情想要問你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.23,0:14:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我老實回答吧 變革者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM的臨界時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲~!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.37,0:14:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會把准尉給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來在那裡嗎!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.35,0:14:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德雷少尉!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這部機體...是增援嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.82,0:14:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼殺了大佐!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.01,0:14:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮瑞斯准尉!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.31,0:14:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你還活著!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.26,0:15:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.91,0:15:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是叛徒嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.79,0:15:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這台詞是該你說的嗎!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.19,0:15:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.02,0:15:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然又來增援!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.86,0:15:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要撤了 准尉!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.07,0:15:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了!瑪麗!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.84,0:15:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別來妨礙我!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.24,0:15:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要為大佐報仇!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.79,0:15:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.42,0:15:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.22,0:15:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算報了仇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會有任何人再活過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只會再增添悲傷而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.72,0:15:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為這種事大家才越來越怪異
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.33,0:15:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被可悲地束縛著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.76,0:16:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連前進的腳步都無法邁出...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是場鬧劇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.78,0:16:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此跛腳的打斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.59,0:16:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒絕成為我的勁敵嗎...少年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.32,0:16:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我自有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.61,0:16:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這裡來的話已經可以安心了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩琳 我們接下來要...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在向事前和克勞斯決定好的匯合地點前進
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.37,0:16:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們先在前面的小屋等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.99,0:16:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能拿起槍的話 只會拖我的後腿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.67,0:16:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好照看孩子們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.27,0:17:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.01,0:17:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KATARON是在戰斗著的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.76,0:17:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.24,0:17:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會戰斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.58,0:17:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了把露易絲找回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.76,0:17:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要 進行我的戰斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮瑞斯中尉在天行者組織裡...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.76,0:18:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說父親不知從多早之前就開始背叛了軍隊...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.15,0:18:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念無法切斷嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就讓我來實現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.24,0:18:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所期待的事情...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.34,0:18:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的願望...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.40,0:18:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半數以上的MS被擊落
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡維爾大尉竟然成了敵人的俘虜?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.76,0:18:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說中的特權成員也沒想象中那麼厲害嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.73,0:18:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是不理解啊 我們的行事方法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.97,0:18:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是指這副慘狀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.39,0:18:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次的作戰 只需要讓我們出擊就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.23,0:18:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 口氣不小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 期待你們的戰果咯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.07,0:18:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:18:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這家伙就是變革者嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.59,0:18:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.25,0:19:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能把頭盔摘下來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.76,0:19:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面 天行者的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.25,0:19:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是 裡瓦爾·裡維爾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是變革者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.56,0:19:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能說說關於你們變革者的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.72,0:19:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.61,0:19:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯!? 艾紐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.30,0:19:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏離預定路線了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.49,0:19:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修正一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.05,0:19:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊... 艾紐!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡特納小姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.06,0:19:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要干什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.28,0:19:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要干什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.82,0:19:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是明擺著的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.52,0:19:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.59,0:19:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變革者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.86,0:21:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OO Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.91,0:21:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該由我駕駛才合適
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.11,0:21:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也這麼覺得吧 裡傑諾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.74,0:21:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然咯 裡本斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.29,0:21:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵 說這種心口不一的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.41,0:21:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ptolemaios還沒有聯絡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.11,0:21:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.54,0:21:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.98,0:21:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把維塔的位置告訴天行者組織的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.23,0:22:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變革者的計劃應該就會被攪亂...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.09,0:22:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後世界就又會...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.07,0:22:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.85,0:22:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.33,0:22:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦艇的操作... 啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.36,0:22:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法控制了...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.96,0:22:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼一回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.83,0:22:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不清楚 但系統全部被刪除了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.09,0:22:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.49,0:22:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是 維塔在介入!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.82,0:22:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫淘氣過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.91,0:22:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再敢擅自亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.93,0:22:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己清楚下場的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.54,0:22:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全無法控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.41,0:22:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫離這裡 准備小型艇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.84,0:22:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行!艦艇所有的系統都沒有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.71,0:22:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵呵...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.31,0:22:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.30,0:22:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜·崔尼蒂 聽得到嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.40,0:22:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這部艦艇的系統無法控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.66,0:22:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.13,0:22:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.30,0:22:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就知道的哦 這件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.46,0:22:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為就是我做的哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.61,0:22:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你... 你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.03,0:22:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屏幕上...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.85,0:23:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.65,0:23:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明什麼都有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.74,0:23:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻還想要 還想要再多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.51,0:23:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內涵什麼的 卻完全沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.00,0:23:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.72,0:23:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對這樣子的您一直都很討厭哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.52,0:23:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.17,0:23:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.91,0:23:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.32,0:23:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了世界的...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.31,0:23:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留美!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.15,0:23:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變革才...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.12,0:23:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.61,0:23:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 爽的受不了!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.05,0:24:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為變革者覺醒的艾紐計劃強奪OO
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.14,0:24:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 艾紐·回歸
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.13,0:24:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欲歸於故鄉 還是所愛的男人...




